", "source": "taxonomy-species-stercorarius-chilensis", "target": "taxonomy-genus-stercorarius", "relation": "belongs_to_genus", "label": "属于属", "evidence": "依据 birds.csv 分类字段补充：Chilean skua 属于属 贼鸥属。"}]}
